<title>ạsm ḥbybk ạ̹yh</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- ạsm ḥbybk ạ̹yh ạsm ḥbyby yswʿ
 byth fyn sạkn fyn fy ạ̉ḥly̱ ạlrbwʿ
 ạlqrạr - rạyḥ rạyḥ ʿly̱ fyn ʿ ạlsmạ ʿly̱ ṭwl
 rạyḥ rạyḥ rạyḥ mhmạ tqwl
 2- ḥby lh yzyd kl ṣbạḥ jdyd
 hw ḥbyby ạlly ạsẖtrạny wạ̉ʿṭạny ạltjdyd
 3- lw ftḥt ạlbạb ydkẖl ʿly̱ ṭwl
 ytʿsẖy̱ mʿạk wạ̹nt mʿạh wyqwl lk mbrwk
 4- wbʿd ạlmsẖwạr ndkẖl ạldyạr
 hạnʿysẖ wyạh wnḥyạ mʿạh dwmạaⁿ fy ạntṣạr
 5- ạ̹nt hạtkẖdm myn ạ̉nạ hạkẖdm yswʿ
 myn byfrḥ qlby hw wymsḥ ly ạldmwʿ
 6- hạnʿysẖ fy htạf ywm ạlạkẖtṭạf
 wạ̉sẖwf bʿyny yswʿ ḥbyby wytm ạlzfạf</lyrics>
</song>